                        <interp inst="t18410201-name-661" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM HERSEY</persName>
                  </hi>. I went to the till at eleven o'clock, there was then 7<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 8<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. in silver in it—I was called down about one, and 4<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. was gone.</p>
               <p>
